12:28.332 --> 12:34.004
I'm here to tell you about my latestand greatest invention,

12:34.087 --> 12:37.382
the Bountiful Belt 3,000.

12:37.466 --> 12:39.051
-I want one.-Look at that.

12:39.134 --> 12:40.469
